snippet.title: PES 2019 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play The Beautiful Game. Create Magic Moments. Feel The Power of Football. This is #PES2019. ESRB Rating: EVERYONE

Visit the PES 2019 website to order your copy of the full game now and get more information:
https://www.konami.com/wepes/2019/

Also, check out our websites and social media channels:
http://www.facebook.com/PES
http://www.twitter.com/officialpes
